<div class="min-h-screen bg-white">
  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="bg-brand-dark py-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center">
          <img src={~p"/images/rsolv_logo_transparent.png"} alt="RSOLV Logo" class="h-10" />
          <span class="text-white text-2xl font-bold ml-3">RSOLV</span>
        </a>
        <nav>
          <a href="/" class="text-white hover:text-brand-green transition-colors">‚Üê Back to Home</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Privacy Content -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
          Last Updated: May 30, 2025
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">1. Our Commitment to Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          At RSOLV, we take your privacy seriously. This policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and your rights regarding your data.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">2.1 Account Information</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 ml-4">
          <li>Email address</li>
          <li>Company name (optional)</li>
          <li>Platform preferences (GitHub, Jira, Linear, etc.)</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">2.2 Repository Data</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 ml-4">
          <li>Repository metadata (names, languages used)</li>
          <li>Issue content and metadata</li>
          <li>Generated pull requests and fixes</li>
          <li>Code snippets relevant to issues being resolved</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">2.3 Usage Data</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 ml-4">
          <li>Fix deployment status</li>
          <li>Feature usage patterns</li>
          <li>Performance metrics</li>
          <li>Error logs related to your account</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">2.4 Analytics Data</h3>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We use privacy-focused analytics (Plausible and SimpleAnalytics) that don't use cookies or track personal information.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        
        <p class="mb-4">We use your information to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 ml-4">
          <li>Provide the RSOLV service</li>
          <li>Generate fixes for your issues</li>
          <li>Improve our security patterns and AI models</li>
          <li>Send service-related communications</li>
          <li>Process billing for deployed fixes</li>
          <li>Provide customer support</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">4. Data Security</h2>
        
        <p class="mb-4">We implement industry-standard security measures including:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 ml-4">
          <li>Encryption of data in transit and at rest</li>
          <li>Regular security audits</li>
          <li>Access controls and authentication</li>
          <li>Secure infrastructure on major cloud providers</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">5. Data Sharing</h2>
        
        <p class="mb-4">We <strong>never</strong> sell your data. We only share information:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 ml-4">
          <li>With your explicit consent</li>
          <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
          <li>With service providers who help us operate RSOLV (under strict confidentiality agreements)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">6. Your Rights</h2>
        
        <p class="mb-4">You have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 ml-4">
          <li>Access your personal data</li>
          <li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Export your data</li>
          <li>Opt out of marketing communications</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">7. Data Retention</h2>
        
        <p class="mb-4">
          We retain your data only as long as necessary to provide our service. Specifically:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 ml-4">
          <li>Account data: Until you close your account</li>
          <li>Fix history: 90 days after deployment</li>
          <li>Billing records: As required by law (typically 7 years)</li>
          <li>Analytics data: Aggregated and anonymized after 30 days</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">8. Third-Party Services</h2>
        
        <p class="mb-4">We use the following third-party services:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 ml-4">
          <li><strong>ConvertKit</strong>: Email communications</li>
          <li><strong>Stripe</strong>: Payment processing (we don't store card details)</li>
          <li><strong>Plausible/SimpleAnalytics</strong>: Privacy-focused analytics</li>
          <li><strong>AI Providers</strong>: For generating fixes (code is processed but not stored by providers)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">9. Cookies</h2>
        
        <p class="mb-4">
          We use minimal, essential cookies only for:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 ml-4">
          <li>Maintaining your session</li>
          <li>Security purposes</li>
          <li>Remembering your preferences</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We don't use tracking or advertising cookies.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">10. Children's Privacy</h2>
        
        <p class="mb-4">
          RSOLV is not intended for users under 13 years of age. We don't knowingly collect information from children.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">11. International Data Transfers</h2>
        
        <p class="mb-4">
          Your data may be processed in the United States. We ensure appropriate safeguards are in place for international transfers.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">12. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        
        <p class="mb-4">
          We'll notify you of any material changes to this privacy policy via email at least 30 days before they take effect.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">13. Contact Us</h2>
        
        <p class="mb-4">
          For privacy-related questions or to exercise your rights:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-none mb-4 ml-4">
          <li>Email: privacy@rsolv.dev</li>
          <li>Address: RSOLV, Inc., Denver, Colorado</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="bg-brand-light p-6 rounded-lg mt-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-brand-dark">Your Privacy Matters</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-dark">
            We believe in transparency and minimal data collection. We only collect what's necessary to provide you with an excellent service, and we never monetize your data.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>